    "body": "Don't Fuck With The Witch / Witch Bizness is a 5 minute / 5 section record, released 28 July 2011 composed of samples from Da Hip Hop Witch, a low-budget film featuring Eminem, Ja Rule, Mobb Deep, Pras, Rah Digga, Vitamin C, and Vanilla Ice, among others.\n\nI made the music and the cover art.\n"
