    "tagline": "Desktop Background",
    "slug": "heads",
    "body": "```ruby\ndef flip(n,chance_of_one,one,two)\n  a = Array.new\n  (0..n).each do\n    if rand <= chance_of_one\n      a.push(one)\n    else\n      a.push(two)\n    end\n  end\n  return a\nend\n```\n"
